  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "キャデラックは、ポーカーのルールを使用したパズル/カードゲームのハイブリッドです。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Cadillac is a match-three card/puzzle game hybrid released by Hect first for the Japanese Famicom and later for the PlayStation. It uses a five by five grid in which the player must position playing cards in order to create sets of three, which are then removed.\n\nThe game uses a casino theme, with the game grid resembling a green felt poker table.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    }
  ],
